@node FALSE "False Orders"

@{b}False Orders@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = A/B/UL(C)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = R
Artist  = Anson Maddocks

Text(UL): You decide whether and how one defending creature blocks, though
          you can't make a choice the defender couldn't legally make. Play
          after defender has chosen defense but before damage has been
          dealt.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_F.guide/FALSE}

@endnode
@node RAGIN "Raging River"

@{b}Raging River@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = A/B/UL(R)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = RR
Artist  = Sandra Everingham

Text(UL): When you attack, non-flying defending creatures must be divided
          as opponent wishes between the left and right sides of the River.
          You then choose on which side of the river to place each
          attacking creature, and attacking creatures can only be blocked
          by flying creatures or those on the same side of the River.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_R.guide/RAGRI}

@endnode
